VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And if you don\'t want to use a template, you can even design your own PPT by adding images and text to a blank clip. Whether you\'re a beginner or a pro, this feature is super easy to use. Second, we\'ve added multiple view'

[03:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'modes to make editing even more flexible and userfriendly. You can switch between these views in the bottom right corner of the generate interface. Here\'s what\'s new. Studio mode. This shows a realtime'

