AUDIO: 'duration. This is perfect if you have a bit more experience and want finer control over your shots. Select a camera track, then drag the edge of the track left or right to adjust how long the'

[04:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'shot holds. If you can\'t drag it yet, click the split icon at the top left of the timeline to enable shot splitting. Once it\'s active, click the track again to split the shot. Then you\'re free to fine-tune the duration however you like.'

[05:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And here\'s a bonus. We\'ve optimized the camera shots preview logic. That means you can now see your changes instantly. No need to regenerate the whole video. Just preview your new camera work. It\'s'

[05:20] [scene:talk]
