AUDIO: 'faster, smoother, and much more efficient. Finally, let\'s take a look at the feature improvements. First, we\'ve added automatic extraction of PPT notes. Have you ever had a fully prepared PPT'

[05:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with speaker notes written for every slide, but once you upload it, you still had to manually copy and paste all the text into the script boxes? It\'s timeconuming and repetitive, right? Well, not anymore. With this update,'

[05:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'we\'ve improved how Rendor reads your PPT files. If your PPT includes notes, the system will now automatically detect and extract that information. When you add the slide to your video, the notes will'

[05:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'instantly appear in the script box. No need to retype or copy paste anything. Second, you now have flexible layout controls in the creation area. In the generate interface, just move your mouse to the edge of the material panel.'

